{MPLTEXT 1 0 225 "# Liapunov Stability. A fixed point x* is Liapunov s
table if all trajectories that start sufficiently close to x* remain c
lose to it for all time. Figs a-d, origin is Liapunov stable, with d N
OT attracting (neutrally stable)." }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" 
