rom trace tau and determinant delta.lambda_1 = 2, lambda_2 = -3." }}}
{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 67 "# eigenvectors (1,1) and (1,
-4) give stable and unstable manifolds." }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" 
